{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>WITNESS THE DAWN! A new horror stirs in The American West.  Survive as one of two characters, solo, or together with a friend.</strong></i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>It was just supposed to be another ordinary night. A storm raging outside, rain tapping on the windows - when suddenly - a banging at the door.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2014</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Following the events of<strong> DAWN: CALM BEFORE THE STORM DEMO, </strong>with limited power restored to the facility - play solo as either 1 of 2 characters, or cooperatively with a friend, and cautiously make your way to the lower levels of the now desolate complex.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198880/extras/Every_dream.png?t=1730306407\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Continuing the story as Trey, or as his \u201ccolleague\u201d, your goal will be to access the lower floors, and find a way to escape. Unfortunately for you, the front door is locked, and the correct key must be found in order to open it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you explore the facility, you\u2019ll bare witness to what has become of your former workplace; and to those who occupy it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><br>Think fast. Keep safe - and your distance; Work together, or alone, and see if you have what it takes to escape, survive and witness - DAWN.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>All rights reserved - Affinity Gameworks 2024.</i><u> </u></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3198880?t=1730306407","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198880/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1730306407","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198880/0bed4712e33082fd685